import React from 'react';

import {
  Flex,
  Image,
  Menu,
  MenuButton,
  MenuItem,
  MenuList,
} from '@chakra-ui/core';

const Header: React.FC = () => (
  <Flex
    paddingX={6}
    width="100vw"
    height={85}
    backgroundColor="#f5f5f5"
    alignItems="center"
    justifyContent="space-between"
  >
    <Image
      src="http://lafengenharia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/cropped-MARCA_LAFE_CHAPADA.png"
      width={180}
    />

    <Menu>
      <MenuButton width={10} height={10}>
        <Flex
          border="3px solid"
          borderColor="blue.300"
          borderRadius="50%"
          width={10}
          height={10}
        >
          <Image
            borderRadius="50%"
            src="https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/57292850?s=460&u=c239cda75c724d55793087628b4276330ae99942&v=4"
          />
        </Flex>
      </MenuButton>
      <MenuList>
        <MenuItem>Sair</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem>Alterar avatar</MenuItem>
      </MenuList>
    </Menu>
  </Flex>
);

export default Header;
